### This route is responsible for creating a new customer and adding a new account with a zero balance.

```response:200
{
  "message": "Customer created successfully",
  "data": {
    "id": "62dc186ea9133bad62af0356",
    "name": "Milhouse Van Houten",
    "phone": "+1 215-878-3605",
    "createdAt": "2022-07-23T15:49:01.617Z",
    "updatedAt": "2022-07-23T15:49:01.617Z",
    "accountId": "62dc186da9133bad62af0355"
  }
}
```

```response:400
{
  "error": "The customer name field cannot be null"
}
```

```response:401
{
  "error": "Customer already exists"
}
```

### This route is responsible for listing all of a customer's data, such as account and transactions.

```response:200
{
  "message": "Customer successfully found",
  "data": {
    "id": "62dbaaf2758170c17db58931",
    "name": "Homer Simpson",
    "phone": "+1 215-878-3600",
    "createdAt": "2022-07-23T08:01:54.256Z",
    "updatedAt": "2022-07-23T08:01:54.256Z",
    "accountId": "62dbaaf2758170c17db58930",
    "account": {
      "id": "62dbaaf2758170c17db58930",
      "balance": 320,
      "createdAt": "2022-07-23T08:01:54.256Z",
      "updatedAt": "2022-07-23T08:09:32.220Z"
    },
    "transactions": [
      {
        "id": "62dbab4e758170c17db58939",
        "amount": 500,
        "methodPayment": "DEBIT",
        "operation": "DEPOSIT",
        "createdAt": "2022-07-23T08:03:26.634Z",
        "updatedAt": "2022-07-23T08:03:26.634Z",
        "customerId": "62dbaaf2758170c17db58931"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

```response:400
{
  "error": "Error, expected a valid object-id"
}
```

```response:401
{
  "error": "Customer does not exists"
}
```

